.env
.local/
.researchos/
*.log
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
local-cache/*
!local-cache/README.md
local-cache/project-specific/

# Private literature corpus and generated evidence stores.
# The public repository should keep templates and instructions, not real Zotero
# databases, normalized full text, reading cards, or project-specific indexes.
corpus/zotero/**
corpus/fulltext/**
corpus/fulltext*/**
corpus/reading-cards/**
!corpus/
!corpus/README.md
!corpus/reading-cards/
!corpus/reading-cards/README.md

# System reports are generated from a local library or local projects.
docs/reports/**
!docs/reports/
!docs/reports/README.md

# 真实配置应放在本机目录或同步私有目录；configs/ 只保留可复用样例。
configs/active_project.yml
configs/project_registry.yml
configs/machine_config.json
configs/easyscholar_api.yml
configs/zotero_governance_rules.json

# Generated research outputs and Zotero exports are runtime artifacts, not core assistant assets.
outputs/
!outputs/
outputs/*
!outputs/README.md
*.bak
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local project workspaces must live outside this framework repository unless
# they are intentionally created as public examples.
.research/
.paper/
01-reading-cards/
02-literature-matrix/
03-manuscript/
04-reviewer-response/
05-ai-code-workspace/

# Obsidian user/session state. Keep reusable vault defaults tracked, but not local window state or plugins.
**/.obsidian/workspace*.json
**/.obsidian/cache/
**/.obsidian/plugins/
